GOVERNMENT OF INDIA(BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT(MANTRIMAND AL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 26th September, 1986
The undersigned is directed to say that with
effect from today, the 26th September, 1986 Shri V.N.
Gadgil, Minister of State (Independent charge) of the
Ministry of Information & Broadcasting assumed also
temporarily additional charge of the Ministry of
Communications till Shri Ram Niwas Mirdha resumes charge
of the office of the Minister of State (Independent
charge) in the Ministry of Communications.
( H.R. Goel )
for Cabinet Secretary
